ISLAMABAD, Mar 06 (APP): Minister of State for Information and Broadcasting Farrukh Habib Sunday said Prime Minister Imran Khan will address a large public meeting in Vehari, Melsi district as part of his mass contact campaign.
After Central Punjab, Mandi Bahauddin, today the people of South Punjab, will also give a warm welcome in Vehari to their beloved leader Imran Khan, he tweeted.
